Title: Veet Full Body Waxing Kit (Dry Skin)
Description: If you want a quick and fuss-free way to remove stubborn body hair, you can ditch your old waxing kit for this pack of Veet full body waxing kit. Smooth skin for up to 4 weeks The special Easy Grip tab of these waxing strips help pull out hair as short as 1.5mm hair from the roots, leaving you with skin that is smooth and exfoliated. With regular use, your hair begins to get lesser, finer, and softer. Suitable for dry skin Formulated with Aloe Vera and enriched with the moisturizing benefits of Lotus Flower, each of the 20 wax strips in this pack is food for dry skin. How To Use: Step 1 - Rub the wax strip between your hands so it’s easy to separate. Step 2 - Test the product on your legs before moving on to sensitive areas like your underarms and bikini line, if it’s your first experience with waxing. For use on the underarm, cut the strips into suitable sizes and make the area taunt by lifting your elbow up. Place the strips in different directions, keeping in mind the opposite directions in which hair on the upper and lower part of the underarm grow. For use on the bikini line, cut the strips into suitable sizes and be sure to only use on small areas at a time. For best results: Thoroughly wash your skin with soap and water before waxing. Pull back the wax strip against the direction of hair growth, to completely uproot them. The wax strips can be reused until they lose their stickiness. Precautions: 1) Please read and retain the outer packaging that has full precautions and directions for use. 2) This product is suitable for use on legs, arms, underarms and bikini line. 3) This product is NOT suitable for use on the head, face, eyes, nose, ears, around the anus, genitals and nipples. 4) Do not use this product on varicose veins, scars, moles, spotty, broken, irritated or sunburnt skin. Avoid use if your skin has had an adverse reaction to waxing in the past. 5) Please give a gap of at least 72 hours between hair removal sessions. 6) Hair should be between 2mm and 5mm long for you to have a comfortable waxing session. You can trim the hair with scissors before waxing if it’s longer. 7) If you are taking medication which can affect skin, or if you suffer from any skin-related disorder, please consult your doctor before using this product. 8) Before every use, test your skin’s reaction to the product by using it on a small area. If there is no adverse reaction after 24 hours, you may continue to use it. 9) If you experience any smarting/tingling sensation while using the product, remove it immediately and rinse thoroughly with cold water. If a burning sensation persists, please seek medical advice. 10) Avoid scratching the skin where the product has been used. 11) Please wait 24 hours before using antiperspirants, perfumed products and artificial tanning equipment, or swimming or sunbathing. 12) Please keep the product out of reach of children. In case of ingestion, please seek immediate medical advice and produce the outer packaging of the product. 13) The product should not come in contact with eyes, but if it does, rinse with plenty of water and seek medical advice immediately.
